25:24.990 --> 25:30.161 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MICK MULVANEY: We are not
kicking anybody
off of any program who really
needs it.

25:30.195 --> 25:34.599 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
