25:36.067 --> 25:37.802 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
And we will do that.

25:37.836 --> 25:41.072 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
We don't have enough money to
take care of
people, everybody, who doesn't
need help.

25:41.106 --> 25:43.308 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
LISA DESJARDINS: Democrats see
it very differently.

25:43.341 --> 25:45.210 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
