recommendations.

26:51.309 --> 26:56.181 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
LISA DESJARDINS: A
recommendation that is
this president's fullest
expression yet of

26:56.214 --> 26:58.950 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
