change.

26:58.984 --> 27:01.086 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
For the "PBS NewsHour," I'm Lisa
Desjardins.

27:01.119 --> 27:05.790 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: There's no
