direction at 100
miles an hour.

27:56.875 --> 27:58.677 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: Chris Edwards?

27:58.710 --> 28:00.345 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
CHRIS EDWARDS, Director of Tax
Policy Studies,
Cato Institute: Yes, I think
there is a lot

28:00.378 --> 28:01.546 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
