number of years
if we don't do anything about
it.

28:09.421 --> 28:13.224 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
The federal debt doubled under
the last president.

28:13.258 --> 28:14.859 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
