that fairy
dust.

29:14.319 --> 29:16.054 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: Go ahead.

29:16.087 --> 29:18.623 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
CHRIS EDWARDS: I agree that
there is some
smoke and mirrors in this
budget, as there

29:18.656 --> 29:21.025 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
