37:35.686 --> 37:41.058 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
DONALD TRUMP: Words can never
describe the
bottomless depths of that evil
or the scope

37:41.092 --> 37:44.962 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
