37:44.996 --> 37:46.864 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
It was history's darkest hour.

37:46.897 --> 37:52.169 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JOHN YANG: He signed the guest
book: "It is
a great honor to be here with
all of my friends.

37:52.203 --> 37:56.707 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
So amazing, and will never
forget."

37:56.741 --> 38:02.079 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Mr. Trump's whirlwind tour of
one of the Middle
East's most intractable problems
ended with

38:02.113 --> 38:03.714 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
