Rome, where,
tomorrow, he is to meet Pope
Francis.

38:08.719 --> 38:11.622 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
For the "PBS NewsHour," I'm John
Yang.

38:11.656 --> 38:15.259 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: As John just
